name: Sands of Sahara
description:
Vast, Open, Limitless and SILENT


They say theres 1,504,000,000,000,000,000,000,000 grains of sand in the Sahara desert. Thats been compared to the number of stars, planets and galaxies in space. We humans are merely inhabiting a grain of sand. Just like grains of sand one day we too will blow away and disappear making way for the next formation or wave of new life and germination.
